1. *Ovoliko* vremena nije dovoljno da bih sve uradio. (This much time is not enough for me to do everything.)

2. Svi smo se slozili da *ovoliko* ne može da se uradi. (We all agreed that this much cannot be done.)

3. *Ovoliko* detalja je izvan našeg domašaja. (This many details are beyond our reach.)

4. Ne možeš da se nadaš da ćeš zaraditi toliko i *ovoliko*. (You can't expect to earn so much and this much.)

5. Znamo da će biti *ovoliko* problema. (We know that there will be this many problems.)

6. *Ovoliko* je dovoljno da se razume. (This much is enough to understand.)